## Mini Project: Public API Client (GitHub User Info)

		We’ll call GitHub’s public API:
		
		https://api.github.com/users/{username}

		It returns JSON like:
		{
		"login": "octocat",
		"id": 583231,
		"public_repos": 8
		}

		We’ll:
		Call API
		Parse JSON
		Print data


You’ll use this when:

	Calling payment gateway
	Calling stock price API
	Calling weather API
	Calling AI model API
	Calling internal microservice

Same pattern every time.